@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-10 offset-lg-1">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-dark border-bottom pb-3 mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <p class="lead text-secondary mb-5">
            This is how we use your personal details:
        </p>

        <section class="mb-5">
            <h3 class="fw-bold">1. Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>To provide efficient management services, this application processes the following types of employee data:</p>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-3">
                <li class="list-group-item bg-light border-0">• Personal Identification (Full Name)</li>
                <li class="list-group-item bg-light border-0">• Country Details (Your home country)</li>
                <li class="list-group-item bg-light border-0">• Gender Data </li>
                <li class="list-group-item bg-light border-0">• Contact Information (Email, Phone Number)</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-5">
            <h3 class="fw-bold">2. How We Use This Information</h3>
            <p>The collected data is used for internal administrative purposes like:</p>
            <div class="row mt-3 text-center">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-white shadow-sm">
                        <h6 class="fw-bold">Resource Tracking</h6>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Managing team structures.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-white shadow-sm">
                        <h6 class="fw-bold">International Support</h6>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Organizing data by countries.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3 border rounded bg-white shadow-sm">
                        <h6 class="fw-bold">Record Keeping</h6>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Historical data archiving.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-5">
            <h3 class="fw-bold">3. Data Security & Storage</h3>
            <p>
                We prioritize the security of your data. All records are stored in a secure database protected by modern encryption standards provided by the <strong>ASP.NET Core</strong> framework. Access is restricted to authorized administrative users only.
            </p>
        </section>
